title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 23 2022

description:
More evidence covid originated in Chinese lab. Only 26% of Americans want U.S. involved in Ukraine. Ian Miller graph on Iceland covid caseload. Governor Glenn Youngkin joins Clay and Buck to discuss how he's delivering on his promises to Virginia. Youngkin template for GOP candidates. C&B review the Trump interview and take a call from California to close the show.
